---
---

<section class="py-24 bg-stone-900 dark:bg-zinc-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-stone-600 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-stone-700 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative">
    <div class="bg-stone-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-16 border border-stone-700 dark:border-zinc-800">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-stone-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-stone-300 dark:text-zinc-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-100 dark:text-stone-100 mb-4">
        מדריך חינם: בנה CRM AI משלך ב-10 דקות
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-300 dark:text-stone-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        למד בדיוק איך להקים מערכת CRM מונעת AI פשוטה שלוכדת לידים ומאוטמטת מעקבים
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center max-w-lg mx-auto">
        <input 
          type="email" 
          placeholder="הכנס את האימייל שלך" 
          class="flex-1 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl bg-stone-900 dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-stone-600 dark:border-zinc-700 text-stone-100 dark:text-stone-100 placeholder-stone-400 dark:placeholder-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-stone-500 dark:focus:ring-zinc-600"
        />
        <button class="bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-200 text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-stone-200 dark:hover:bg-white transition-all whitespace-nowrap">
          קבל את המדריך
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-400 dark:text-zinc-500 mt-6">
        ללא ספאם, רק תובנות אוטומציה שימושיות
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
